{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Game AR Ingress Akan Merambah Dunia Anime","content":"<p>Sebelum orang mengenal <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/pokemon-go-genap-satu-tahun-habis-ini-apa/\">Pokemon GO</a>, ada game yang bernama Ingress. Dirilis perdana untuk ponsel Android di tahun 2013, Ingress merupakan salah satu pelopor game <em>alternate reality</em> (AR) yang menyajikan sebuah permainan <em>multiplayer</em> berbalut teknologi GPS dan <em>geotagging</em>. Para pemain yang berada dalam dua kubu berbeda harus bertarung untuk memperebutkan kekuasaan dari lokasi dunia nyata seperti mal, monumen, dan lain sebagainya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44891\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44891\" data-attachment-id=\"44891\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/attachment/01-ingress-game/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ingress-game\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44891\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game.jpg\" alt=\"01-ingress-game\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-ingress-game-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44891\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gamer harus mengunjungi lokasi tertentu untuk bisa bermain Ingress. (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div>\n<p>Pemain Ingress merupakan salah satu komunitas <em>gamer</em> yang sangat solid. Di seluruh dunia diadakan <em>gathering</em> para <em>gamer</em> dimana mereka menjelajahi kota untuk bermain bersama. Meskipun berada dalam kubu berbeda, setiap <em>gamer</em> saling menghargai lawan mereka dan tak ragu untuk saling menolong.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44892\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44892\" data-attachment-id=\"44892\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/attachment/02-ingress-event/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ingress-event\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44892\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event.jpg\" alt=\"02-ingress-event\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-ingress-event-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44892\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Event Ingress yang diadakan di Jepang. (Sumber: Wireless Watch Japan)</p></div>\n<p>Untuk semakin memperkuat popularitasnya, Niantic sebagai pembuat game Ingress dan Pokemon GO akan memproduksi adaptasi <em>anime</em> dari Ingress. “Saya sangat suka membangun sebuah dunia lewat berbagai jenis media,” tutur CEO dari Niantic, John Hanke. “…<em>Anime</em> merupakan jalan yang sangat bagus untuk mengenalkan Ingress, karena kamu bisa membuat orang tertarik dengan dunia yang berbeda dari yang sehari-hari kita jalani,” tambahnya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44893\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44893\" data-attachment-id=\"44893\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/attachment/03-ingress-map/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ingress-map\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44893\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map.jpg\" alt=\"03-ingress-map\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-ingress-map-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44893\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">03-ingress-mapGamer bisa memeriksa daerah kekuasaan Enlightened dan Resistance di komputer. (Sumber: CNET)</p></div>\n<p>Sebelumnya, Niantic sudah merilis berbagai <em>e-book</em> dan <em>webseries</em> yang bertujuan sebagai perkenalan akan dunia Ingress. Dalam setiap cerita Ingress, terdapat sebuah energi atau unsur zat baru bernama Exotic Matter (XM). Penemuan XM di seluruh penjuru bumi ternyata berhubungan dengan Shapers, sosok alien misterius. Manusia terbagi menjadi dua kubu berbeda: Enlghtened yang ingin menggunakan XM untuk membuka potensi evolusi manusia, sementara kubu Resistance berusaha menjaga XM yang ternyata melindungi manusia dari Shapers.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44894\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44894\" data-attachment-id=\"44894\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/attachment/04-ingress-manga/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-ingress-manga\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44894\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga.jpg\" alt=\"04-ingress-manga\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-ingress-manga-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44894\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Dua judul manga Ingress yang sudah terbit. (Sumber: MyAnimeList)</p></div>\n<p>Pertanyaannya, kenapa <em>anime</em>? Percaya atau tidak, Ingress memiliki popularitas yang besar di Jepang. Sudah ada berbagai <em>event garthering</em> yang diadakan di Jepang, bekerja sama dengan berbagai perusahaan terkemuka. Bahkan salah satu <em>event</em> di Jepang pada tahun 2014 diabadikan dalam sebuah <em>manga</em> berjudul Ingress: Tokyo Anomaly. Ada lagi satu <em>manga</em> Ingress berjudul Ingress-teki Nichijou, yang menceritakan pertemuan antara Ibuki dengan gadis bule bernama Chloe. Tak disangka, Chloe sebenarnya adalah seorang agen Ingress.</p>\n<p><iframe style=\"border: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FIngress%2Fvideos%2F1673827422664917%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Dengan alasan di atas, rasanya tak ada keluhan dengan adaptasi <em>anime</em> ini. <em>Anime</em> Ingress akan tayang mulai bulan Oktober 2018 di blok siaran +Ultra milik Fuji TV. Studio animasi Craftar akan memproduksi <em>anime</em>nya.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44895\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44895\" data-attachment-id=\"44895\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-ingress-game-alternate-reality/attachment/05-ingress-prime/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-ingress-prime\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44895\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime.jpg\" alt=\"05-ingress-prime\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-ingress-prime-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44895\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Konsep tampilan game Ingress Prime. (Sumber: Youtube)</p></div>\n<p>Belum ada informasi lebih terkait jalan cerita <em>anime</em> Ingress ini, namun diyakini bahwa <em>anime</em> Ingress akan menampilkan cerita baru yang terinspirasi dari Ingress Prime. Ingress Prime adalah <em>update</em> untuk game Ingress orisinil, yang akan merombak total seluruh permainan Ingress dari nol. Niantic menjanjikan Ingress Prime akan memiliki tampilan baru, cerita baru, dan <em>gimmick</em> baru. Seperti apakah semuanya? Niantic juga belum mau membuka kartu.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sJRX8E-Yy3o\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Sepertinya kita masih harus menunggu info lainnya menjelang penayangan <em>anime</em> Ingress di bulan Oktober nanti. Apa kamu pemain Ingress juga? Kamu kubu Enlightened atau Resistance? Tulis di komentar ya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"02f1268b-dcb2-5936-8db2-da4031a2d456"}}}